         <div type="translation">
 	<p n="1-3">Success! On the tenth day of the fifth fortnight of the hot season in the eighth year of the king Maḍhariputa Svāmisakaseṇa. On the above (date)..</p>
    <p n="3-5">A cave was established of (by) Hālanikā the wife of the market councillor <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"></gap>ti, son of Venhunadi, a resident of Kalyan.</p>
    <p n="5-7">Together with the noble Lā<seg type="component" subtype="vowel"><gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="component"/></seg>i<unclear>na</unclear>, together with….together with the son Dhāmaya…(together with) Buddhakaya, together with…together with…</p>         
         </div>
          
          
          
          
